from dataclasses import dataclass

@dataclass
class Triple:
    subject: str
    predicate: str
    object: str

# EVOLVE-BLOCK-START

def predict(triples: list[Triple]) -> str:
    sentence = ""
    subject = ""
    for triple in triples:
        if not subject:
            subject = triple.subject
            sentence += f"{subject} "

        predicate = triple.predicate
        object_val = triple.object

        predicate_map = {
            "country": "is in {object_val} ",
            "ingredient": "contains {object_val} ",
            "region": "is from the {object_val} region ",
            "capital": "where the capital is {object_val} ",
            "served": "is served {object_val} ",
            "mainIngredient": "is made with {object_val} ",
            "dishVariation": ", which is a variation of {object_val} ",
            "creatorOfDish": ", created by {object_val} ",
            "ethnicGroup": ", and is associated with the {object_val} ",
            "alternativeName": ", also known as {object_val} ",
            "creator": " created by {object_val} ",
            "related": " and is related to {object_val} ",
            "similarDish": " and is similar to {object_val} ",
            "genus": ", which is a {object_val} ",
            "leader": " and its leader is {object_val} ",
            "leaderTitle": " with the leader title of {object_val} ",
            "officialLanguage": " and the official language is {object_val} ",
            "demonym": " and people are known as {object_val} ",
            "currency": " and uses the currency {object_val} ",
            "isPartOf": " which is part of {object_val} ",
            "foundationPlace": " and was founded in {object_val} ",
            "servingTemperature": " and is served {object_val} ",
            "class": " which is a {object_val} ",
            "carbohydrate": " with {object_val}g of carbohydrate ",
            "fat": " and contains {object_val}g of fat ",
            "year": " in the year {object_val} ",
            "protein": " with {object_val}g of protein ",
            "servingSize": " with a serving size of {object_val}g ",
            "order": " which is a member of the {object_val} order ",
            "family": " which belongs to the {object_val} family ",
            "division": " which is a {object_val} division "
        }

        if len(triples) > 1:
            if predicate in ["country", "region"]:
                sentence += predicate_map.get(predicate, f" which is in {object_val} ").format(object_val=object_val)
            elif predicate in ["ingredient", "mainIngredient"]:
                sentence += predicate_map.get(predicate, f" and contains {object_val} ").format(object_val=object_val)
            else:
                sentence += predicate_map.get(predicate, f", {object_val} ").format(object_val=object_val)
        else:
            sentence += predicate_map.get(predicate, f" and its {predicate} is {object_val} ").format(object_val=object_val)

    return sentence.strip() + "."

# EVOLVE-BLOCK-END
